// Example API calls for the new structured data:

### Get Contacts for Program1
GET /Contacts/{{profileId}}/DEMO/PROGRAM1

### Get Addresses for Program1  
GET /Addresses/{{profileId}}/DEMO/PROGRAM1

### Get Submissions for Program1
GET /Submissions/{{profileId}}/DEMO/PROGRAM1

### Get Organizations for Program1
GET /Organizations/{{profileId}}/DEMO/PROGRAM1

### Get Contacts for Program2
GET /Contacts/{{profileId}}/DEMO/PROGRAM2

### Get Addresses for Program2
GET /Addresses/{{profileId}}/DEMO/PROGRAM2

### Get Submissions for Program2  
GET /Submissions/{{profileId}}/DEMO/PROGRAM2

### Get Organizations for Program2
GET /Organizations/{{profileId}}/DEMO/PROGRAM2

### Test with sample profile ID
@profileId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Get Contacts Sample
GET /Contacts/{{profileId}}/DEMO/PROGRAM1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response Structure for Contacts:
// {
//   "profileId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
//   "pluginId": "DEMO", 
//   "provider": "PROGRAM1",
//   "jsonData": "{\"profileId\":\"...\",\"data\":{\"contacts\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"firstName\":\"John\",\"lastName\":\"Doe\",...}]}}",
//   "populatedAt": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
// }